description: Mike Tyka 2017 @mtyka https://www.miketyka.com Series: “Portraits of Imaginary People” https://www.electricartefacts.art/artist/mike-tyka @e_artefacts The series, titled "Portraits of Imaginary People" explores the latent space of human faces by training a generative adversarial neural network (GAN) to imagine and then depict portraits of people who don’t exist.
